{"tid":1563111,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯：與C.朗食晚飯無問題","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:58:15.000Z","uid":173952,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"944cb9903ab885f993a3dd3a4cab2494e0c7a02f","tid":1563111,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"美斯和C.朗拿度<br />\n<br />\n  近日，美斯接受了西班牙《每日體育報》的全球獨家專訪，他回答了記者們提出了關於巴塞、個人和未來的一些問題。<br />\n<br />\n  &mdash;&mdash;C.朗拿度（C.Ronaldo）跟您說要邀請您一起吃晚飯，您會去嗎？會接受他的邀請嗎？<br />\n<br />\n  我沒有問題，我一直都說我和他之間沒有任何問題，我們之前並不是朋友，因為我們沒有共處於一個更衣室中，但我們一直在各種頒獎典禮上見面。我沒有任何問題，在最近一次（歐洲足協）頒獎典禮上，我們甚至聊了更多內容。<br />\n<br />\n  我不知道是否會有（一起吃）晚飯，因為我不知道我們是否有共同的時間，因為每一個人都有自己的私人時間和私人事務，但如果要一起吃晚飯的話，我沒有問題"},{"pid":"41b4c170e96652764afd030d2b70004ef9e327a8","tid":1563111,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d7e42dc63715f1edc978bfbc78debcf33edb3aa2","tid":1563111,"uid":142854,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"食大家樂ok?"},{"pid":"0b1e0e447f957752a099828bfc532f6461638537","tid":1563111,"uid":278434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"屯門有學界人鏈要人<br 